                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-259-off1328 t18280911-259-cd1329"></join>, 1 quadrant, value 20s; 2 shirts, value 4s.: 2 pairs of trousers, value 6s.; 1 frock, value 1s., and 1 pair of drawers, value 1s.
